      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone looking for value. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car does show noticeable cosmetic wear both inside and out, including some minor scratches and seat fading. It has been regularly serviced, though it is approaching a point where some routine suspension work and new tires will be needed. Overall, it is a solid, functional car that reflects its age and mileage honestly.",
