    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any chips or scratches. Inside, the interior is pristine, with leather that remains supple and a cabin that still carries a hint of that new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history. Every feature and electronic component functions flawlessly, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from a brand-new vehicle.",
