      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for a great project opportunity! This vehicle is in poor condition and will need some dedicated TLC and mechanical attention to get back to its best, but it offers a fantastic starting point for a restorer or anyone looking for a budget-friendly way to get on the road. It's a diamond in the rough with plenty of potential for the right owner!",
