    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine condition. This specimen has been meticulously maintained to a showroom standard, reflecting a level of care that is increasingly rare in the pre-owned market. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior appointments, every detail speaks to its uncompromising quality. For the discerning buyer who demands the finest, this offering represents an unparalleled investment in both performance and prestige.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car enthusiast! It honestly breaks my heart a little to let this absolute beauty go, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home. She\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy\u2014pampered like royalty and kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage. The paint has a deep, mirror-like shine that truly has to be seen to be believed, and the interior is so clean it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s a smooth, dream-like ride that\u2019s ready for your next weekend getaway. Come on by for a chat and a look\u2014I\u2019d love to show you why this is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a meticulously sorted specimen, featuring a powertrain that has been maintained to a rigorous stage-zero standard. The forced induction system holds peak boost with zero taper, and the variable valve timing remains exceptionally crisp across the entire rev range. The chassis is remarkably taut, benefiting from a comprehensive suspension refresh that eliminates any hint of bushing deflection. Every fluid has been transitioned to high-temp synthetics, and the drivetrain exhibits zero lash, ensuring immediate power delivery. This is an investment-grade example with a flawless finish and a cabin that retains its factory-fresh tactile feedback. Truly a turn-key machine for the enthusiast who values mechanical transparency and linear performance.",
      "price": 46800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
